{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Date.prototype","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methods</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/@@toPrimitive\"><code>Date.prototype[@@toPrimitive]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getDate\"><code>Date.prototype.getDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getDay\"><code>Date.prototype.getDay()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getHours\"><code>Date.prototype.getHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.getMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.getMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getTime\"><code>Date.prototype.getTime()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getTimezoneOffset\"><code>Date.prototype.getTimezoneOffset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCDate\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCDay\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCDay()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCHours\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/now\"><code>Date.now()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/parse\"><code>Date.parse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setDate\"><code>Date.prototype.setDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setHours\"><code>Date.prototype.setHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.setMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.setMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setTime\"><code>Date.prototype.setTime()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCDate\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCHours\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toDateString\"><code>Date.prototype.toDateString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toGMTString\"><code>Date.prototype.toGMTString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toISOString\"><code>Date.prototype.toISOString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toJSON\"><code>Date.prototype.toJSON()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleDateString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleDateString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleTimeString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleTimeString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toString\"><code>Date.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toTimeString\"><code>Date.prototype.toTimeString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toUTCString\"><code>Date.prototype.toUTCString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/UTC\"><code>Date.UTC()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/valueOf\"><code>Date.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Inheritance:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methods</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>Date.prototype</code></strong> 屬性表示 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 建構子的原型。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"header\" colspan=\"2\">Property attributes of <code>Date.prototype</code></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Writable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Enumerable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Configurable</td>\n      <td>yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"描述","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>JavaScript <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 實體繼承自 <code>Date.prototype。你可以藉由改變建構子的原型物件，來影響所有繼承自</code> JavaScript <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 的實體。</p>\n\n<p>為了千年年份（換個說法，考慮現在已到了 2000 年）的相容性，設定上你應該採用完整的年份。舉例來說，使用 1998 而不是 98 。為了讓你能取得完整的年份資料， Javascript 包含了 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear\"><code>getFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ， <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>setFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ， <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear\"><code>getUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 以及 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCFullYear\"><code>setUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法。</p>\n\n<p>自 ECMAScript 6 開始， <code>Date.prototype</code> 物件只是個一般物件，而不是一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 實體。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.constructor\"><code>Date.prototype.constructor</code></dt>\n <dd>回傳一個能建立實體的函數，這是 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 預設的建構子。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"getter","title":"Getter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getdate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getDate\"><code>Date.prototype.getDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間月份中的日期（1-31）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getday\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getDay\"><code>Date.prototype.getDay()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間星期中的日子（0-6）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getfullyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的年份（ 以 4 位數表現）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.gethours_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getHours\"><code>Date.prototype.getHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的小時（0-23）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getmilliseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的毫秒數（0-999）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getminutes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.getMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的分鐘數（0-59）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getmonth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.getMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的月份（0-11）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時間的秒數（0-59)。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.gettime_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getTime\"><code>Date.prototype.getTime()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳由 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC 開始，到代表時間經過的毫秒數（以負值表示 1970 年之前的時間）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.gettimezoneoffset_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getTimezoneOffset\"><code>Date.prototype.getTimezoneOffset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳本地時差為多少分鐘。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcdate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCDate\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的在月份中的日期（1-31）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcday_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCDay\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCDay()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間在星期中的日子（0-6）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcfullyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的年份（ 以 4 位數表現）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutchours_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCHours\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的小時數（0-23）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcmilliseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間裡的毫秒數（0-999）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcminutes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的分鐘數（0-59）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcmonth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的月份數（0-11）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getutcseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳標準時間的秒數（0-59）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.getyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>回本地時間的年份（通常 2-3 位數）。用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear\"><code>getFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 取代。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"setter","title":"Setter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setdate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setDate\"><code>Date.prototype.setDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間月份中的日期。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setfullyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的完整年份（以 4 位數表達 4 位數年份）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.sethours_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setHours\"><code>Date.prototype.setHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的小時數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setmilliseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的毫秒數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setminutes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.setMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的分鐘數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setmonth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.setMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的月份。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的秒數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.settime_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setTime\"><code>Date.prototype.setTime()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定這個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 物件距 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC 的毫秒數，允許使用負值表示之前的時間。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcdate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCDate\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCDate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間月份中的日期。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcfullyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的完整年份（以 4 位數表示 4 位數年分）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutchours_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCHours\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCHours()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的小時數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcmilliseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMilliseconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMilliseconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的毫秒數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcminutes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMinutes\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMinutes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的分鐘數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcmonth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCMonth\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCMonth()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的月份數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setutcseconds_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCSeconds()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>設定標準時間的秒數。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.setyear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>設定本地時間的年份（使用 2-3 位數）。使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>setFullYear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 取代。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conversion_getter","title":"Conversion getter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.todatestring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toDateString\"><code>Date.prototype.toDateString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>以可閱讀的字串型式，回傳 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 的部分資訊。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.toisostring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toISOString\"><code>Date.prototype.toISOString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>將日期時間轉換成 ISO 8601 格式的字串回傳。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tojson_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toJSON\"><code>Date.prototype.toJSON()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳等義於 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 物件使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toISOString\"><code>toISOString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法的結果。特別使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON/stringify\"><code>JSON.stringify()</code></a> 處理。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.togmtstring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toGMTString\"><code>Date.prototype.toGMTString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>回傳 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 以 GMT (UT) 時區基準代表的時間字串。使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toUTCString\"><code>toUTCString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法來取代。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tolocaledatestring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleDateString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleDateString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>依照系統的時間地區設定，回傳日期字串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tolocaleformat\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleFormat()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>傳入格式化字串參數，將日期時間轉換成指定格式的字串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tolocalestring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳依系統的地區設定導出的日期時間字串。覆寫自 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tolocaletimestring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleTimeString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleTimeString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳依系統的地區設定導出的時間字串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tosource_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toString\"><code>Date.prototype.toSource()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>回傳一個建立相同 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 物件的程式碼字串；你可以拿這個結果來建立新物件。覆寫自 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.tostring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toString\"><code>Date.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳代表此 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 物件的字串。覆寫自 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.totimestring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toTimeString\"><code>Date.prototype.toTimeString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>以人類可讀的格式，回傳時間部分的字串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.toutcstring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toUTCString\"><code>Date.prototype.toUTCString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>依 UTC 時區，轉換出時間日期字串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"date.prototype.valueof_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/valueOf\"><code>Date.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>回傳 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> 物件的原始數值。覆寫自 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"規範","title":"規範","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">規範</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">狀態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">註</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%201st%20edition,%20June%201997.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>初步定義。實作在 JavaScript 1.1.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.9.5\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-TW\">The definition of 'Date.prototype' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-properties-of-the-date-prototype-object\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-TW\">The definition of 'Date.prototype' in that spec